{
  "stem": "23506.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was going in-- it was called the German Kaserne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They let me in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I signed my name in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I stayed there with the-- with the baby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, when time was for his food or whatever, I went back home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I will tell you, that I never knew-- see, when you're on the run, you have to know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I already-- when I was in the Bernardino Kaserne, this was a-- a church on the Bernardino Street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the-- and the fathers had a vegetable garden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on one side was a big fence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I already looked, in case something happened, where will be my route to run away?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It'd be better to go through the-- through the church or through the side gate?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every time, I was wearing on my body-- body, 50 zlotys and my passport-- because I already changed the passport-- rolled in, you know, from this-- a pink passport, because I figured it like this.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If something happened, I will run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once I have a-- a passport and 50 zloty, I will be OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I also forgot, when I didn't get the job-- six weeks, I think, or three weeks-- I was running on the trains, from one train to the other.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From one, I was waiting in the-- in the train stations, covered myself up, sit there, and went on another train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "First, that it was safer, cheaper, and easier to spend the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think that I am looking over my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, I figured like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were born in the wrong times in history.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are a actress.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to play your role good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you have to pay one price, it is your life.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
